rows.label: tlk0001024_msg0001
rows.name:
What's with the long face? Are
you seasick or something?

rows.label: tlk0001024_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm just not used to a ship with so
many salvagers on it, that's all!

rows.label: tlk0001024_msg0004
rows.name:
At this rate, you'll be exhausted
by the time we arrive...
